summary: Replaces the vanilla highland cows with normal cows that we all know and love!
descriptionHtml:
This replaces vanilla cow model and textures. 

I made these a while back as part of a project involving farm animals. A couple of guys wanted these files, so i am uploading them here. Textures and model are not perfect yet, kind of a work in progress thing.

If you do like these, let me know. I have already made models for bulls, calves, and sheep. I might get back on working on these if you guys are interested enough. I have a farm animal mod in mind.

Anyways, enjoy these, and if demands are good i will improve textures, and maybe make an av package for it.  

Manual install: put the data folder in your skyrim directory. 

Feel free to check out my other (a bit more serious :p ) mods:

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17723]Birds of Skyrim[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17424]Pets of Skyrim[/url]

Qas
